&lt;p data-start=&quot;96&quot; data-end=&quot;366&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a results-driven Account Executive to grow our federal business and expand our footprint across U.S. government agencies. You’ll own the full sales cycle, helping agencies adopt our data, AI, and analytics platform to solve mission-critical challenges.&amp;nbsp;This role requires deep experience navigating federal procurement, building senior-level relationships, and closing complex, high-value deals. You’ll work closely with internal teams and partners to align solutions with agency priorities and deliver measurable impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
